    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
            <p>Jennifer is a Certified Hotheads Hair Extension Sew-In and Tape-In method extension specialist.</p>

            <p>Sew-in extensions are 100% human hair, hand-tied and machine-tied weft extensions that use no adhesives or heat to damage your hair, are more comfortable to wear and easier to hide then other extension methods. Utilizing Hotheads' non-damaging, sew-in application technique allows stylists to add volume, length, or color safely and comfortably to clients that prefer the industry’s latest cutting-edge method.</p>

            <p>Tape-in extensions are 100% human hair, adhesive weft extensions that are applied without the need for tools or heat. The application is quicker than other methods (less than an hour) and offers more versatility with styling. This method is a great option for people with a smaller budget or shorter term extension needs.</p>

            <p>Sometimes, it is best to combine these two methods to achieve your desired look.</p>

            <p>Hotheads extensions come with a natural body wave that can fit lots of different hair textures.  With over 50 shades and 3 lengths to choose from, there are more than 1,000 color combinations possible when multiple colors are blended together, we will find the right style for you!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
