        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
            <p>Pricing for extensions depends on several factors, including: method of install, color, length, and the amount of hair needed to achieve the desired look. That’s why we always start with a free consultation, where you will leave with an exact quote for your extensions. All clients receiving extensions also get everything you need to care for your new hair - a professional full size shampoo and conditioner set, extension hair brush, a Soulful Scrunchies Satin Jumbo Scrunchie and a professional treatment or styling product so you can keep your new hair tangle free and healthy.</p>
